| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4540 — Recovery Inhibition (alphalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9aa9b072-b76d-5fbb-af60-3aa6a85aed8c"
